dcterms:description: The RSNA 2019 Brain CT Hemorrhage data set was built from scratch for the 2019 RSNA Intracranial Hemorrhage Detection challenge held on Kaggle. It contains CT scans from three institutions and includes 25,272 CT examinations with a total of 870,301 CT slices, labeled by annotators using five brain hemorrhage types.
